{"tid":1807303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英打開了港獨的潘朶拉盒子（2016年9月）","createTime":"2020-01-01T17:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T12:17:32.000Z","uid":172349,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"911ccaae3dfab86aadd2c30d95a1da60cdfaefe9","tid":1807303,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.twreporter.org/a/opinion-hongkong-election-leung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twreporter.org%2Fa%2Fopinion-hongkong-election-leung&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOABURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=b9c81be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twreporter.org/a/opinion-hongkong-election-leung</a><br />\n<br />\n自決及港獨運動，是在梁振英管治下迅速成形，借此次反梁形勢下的選舉正式走入議會。若干年後北京回頭再看，必定追悔不已，因為我認為現時香港市民並不一定是支持自決及港獨理念，而是一種抗議票，是反對粱振英「倒行逆施」，所以選一些夠「硬淨」的人進入議會，與梁振英及共產黨對著幹。梁振英打開了港獨這個潘朶拉盒子，今後北京要再強硬阻止的政治成本愈來愈高，自決獨立運動，或明或暗，或急或緩，都會成為反對運動的主流。<br />\n<br />\n北京如何調整對港政策，已經迫在眉睫，若強硬下去，取消當選有港獨傾向議員資格，立即引起更大規模騷亂。若改弦更張，「窗口」是借明年初舉行的行政長官選舉，拍板換人，以宣示溫和路線，緩和香港內部抗中反梁氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n香港，已到了關鍵時刻！"},{"pid":"51ce92ec47da7ace974092c1987bc640df538c59","tid":1807303,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"689=港獨之父<br />\n連登仔=大中華膠"},{"pid":"0d8eed4f6c635006a089a3041ca1c9c64f8d916d","tid":1807303,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1a96f487945330abce9563d555efbfdc266059d","tid":1807303,"uid":329448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ce92ec47da7ace974092c1987bc640df538c59","tid":1807303,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"689=港獨之父<br />\n連登仔=大中華膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nNmUVwD7hhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnNmUVwD7hhc&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOABURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=92df76c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nNmUVwD7hhc</a>"},{"pid":"be1355c5f54737bd0f2ef2031e0caa5ba0fbcde5","tid":1807303,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa404ab3f1844952f4122c3ede9815834e3c5ca","tid":1807303,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55362889cfa97bdb3d60abbd0b644f323c3330e7","tid":1807303,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d8eed4f6c635006a089a3041ca1c9c64f8d916d","tid":1807303,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"除左第一點駁唔到之外<br />\n<br />\n其他咩姓咩文呀果d 新加坡台灣馬拉都有用緊<br />\n<br />\n咁佢地算唔算都自古以來係支那人？"}]}